From 922ffb5076a353f51f40728a58ef654b3b99a107 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 20:15:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Convert single-page SPA to 3-page site: home/work, visual,
 about

Visual and about are now separate HTML files with their own nav,
cursor, and styles. Home/work remain in index.html with the existing
floating-window and scroll-snap experience. Nav links route between
pages; arriving at index.html#work snaps to the work section.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01QmEbxdVHT1qGpUNNfHtQLc
---
 about.html  | 175 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 index.html  | 104 +++++---------------------
 visual.html | 206 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 398 insertions(+), 87 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 about.html
 create mode 100644 visual.html

